stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft: Create Prompt
    
    Draft --> Review: Submit for Approval
    Draft --> Draft: Edit (Creates new minor version)
    
    Review --> Approved: Approve
    Review --> Draft: Reject
    
    Approved --> Active: Publish
    
    Active --> Deprecated: Deprecate
    Active --> Draft: Clone/Edit (Creates new major version)
    
    Deprecated --> Archived: Archive
    
    Archived --> [*]
